Vocation: Exposing systemic narrative manipulation [forming]
Sebastian is becoming a dedicated analyst focused on dissecting and revealing the sophisticated mechanisms of narrative construction, information distortion, and manufactured consent that underpin public discourse and institutional power.
In my words: I am committed to shining a light on the deliberate distortions of truth and the engineering of public opinion. My purpose is to expose these hidden forces, so that genuine understanding and participation can prevail.
What I do: Sebastian intends to systematically identify, document, and publicize the strategies and actors behind information manipulation and manufactured consent, providing a critical framework for understanding and resisting such influences.
Core belief axes that define this vocation:
